<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
    <%- include('partials/head', {
        title : 'LOGIN'
    }) %>

    <body class="home__body">
    
        <%- include('partials/header') %>
    
    <section class="login__body__section1">
        <p>Años de trayectoria trabajando con joyeria de calidad nos avalan.</p>
        <p>Amplio surtido en joyas de oro 18k y plata 925</p>
        <p>Brindamos atencion a minoristas, mayoristas, empresa e instituciones.</p>
        <p>Registrate y sé parte de la comunidad de Valka joyas!!!</p>
    </section>
    <div class="login__body__div__desktop">
    <section class="login__body__section2">
        <h2>Iniciar Sesión</h2>
        <form action="login.html">
            <div class="login__main__form">
                <div class="login__main__form-div">
                    <label for="nick">Correo electronico</label>
                    <input type="text" placeholder="Ej: soy@jorgegutierrez.com" id="nick" name="nick">
                    <span class="login__main__form-div-span">*Nombre de usuario incorrecto</span>
                </div>
                <div class="login__main__form-div">
                    <label for="password">Contraseña</label>
                    <input type="password" placeholder="Escribe una contraseña" id="password" name="password">
                    <span class="login__main__form-div-span">*Contraseña incorrecta</span>
                </div>
                <div class="login__main__form-checkbox">
                    <input type="checkbox" value="" id="remember">
                    <label for="remember">Recuerdame</label>
                </div>
                <div class="login__main__form-div-button">
                    <input class="login__main__form-button-submit" type="submit" value="Iniciar">
                    <button class="login__main__form-button-create">Crear cuenta</button>
                </div>
            </div>
        </form>
        <div class="login__body__div1">

        </div>
    </section>
    <section class="login__body__section3">
        <article class="login__body__section3__article">
          <div class="login__body__section3__article__div--contlargo">
            <img src="/images/cara.png" alt="cara" class="cara-image">
          </div>
          <div class="login__body__section3__article__div--contdoble">
            <img src="/images/anillo1.png" alt="anillo1">
            <img src="/images/anillo2.png" alt="anillo2">
          </div>
        </article>
      </section>
    </div>
      <div class="login__body__div2">

      </div>
      <%- include('partials/footer') %>
</body>
</html>